    <stitle>ALLISON WT TRANSMISSION ELECTRONIC CONTROLS - ELECTRICAL OPERATION - GROUND SYSTEM</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="operate" graphiccount="0">
        <title>GROUND SYSTEM</title>
        <para>The WT control system has two ground circuits. Circuit (323) grounds the VIM to the same bolt as the
            battery ground strap at flywheel housing. Circuit 144 is an ECU signal ground circuit that is grounded to
            the ECU bracket.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
